# Rust
/target/
**/*.rs.bk
# Cargo.lock IS committed at the workspace root because we ship a binary
# crate (ogentic-audit-cli). Standard Rust convention; required for
# cargo-audit / cargo-deny to lock advisory scans against a specific
# dependency closure rather than re-resolving every run.

# Python
